<font size=2><table width="100%" bgcolor="#004b97"><font color=#d2d200><b>Shield of Bane Warding</b></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=1><a style="color: #ffffff" href="mailto:jcsmith@amazinghideaways.com?subject=Regarding: Shield of Bane Warding">Submit Info</a></font></table>
<font color=white>
MAGIC 
LORE 




<br><br>


<b>Inventory Slots:</b> Secondary
<br>







<b>Armor Class:</b> 25<br>
<b>Modifiers:</b> Cha +8, Wis +20, SV M +12<br>
<b>Size:</b> Medium<br>
<b>Weight:</b> 6.5<br>

<br>
<b>Classes:</b> WAR PAL RNG DRU SHM BST<br>
<b>Races:</b> ALL<br>





<br>




























<br><table width="300" bgcolor="#004b97"><b><font color=#d2d200>Obtained in 
<a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqquestfull&eqquests.quest_name=%22Shield%20of%20Bane%20Warding%22">Shield of Bane Warding</a> Quest</b></font></table><br>
<b>Recommended Level:</b> 50<br>
<b>Starting NPC:</b> Roshawna Rhorer<br><br>

<b>Description</b>:<br>
This is a long and involved quest that results in an excellent reward for wisdom casters.<BR><BR>The spoiler is given in no nonsense format.<BR><BR>1) Tell Roshawna Rhorer(-230, +160) in Katta Castellum that you will "help the souls" and he will give you an eight slot container.<BR><BR>2) Kill Tormented Vah Shir in Tenebrous Mountains until you get eight Tormented Vah Shir Skulls. They spawn at around -1250, +1750. Kill everything in the area to get them to spawn.<BR><BR>3) Once you get eight skulls put them in to the contianer and hit combine. Return the result to Roshwana in Katta and bring a group.<BR><BR>4) After handing in those items a Vah Shir Courier will spawn, but he is a traitor. Wait for him to speak to Roshawna and get the combined box and then kill him and eight Reanimated Vah Shir will spawn. Kill them all and loot all of the corpses. <BR><BR>You will get a new container from the courier and eight new skulls from the reanimated Vah Shirs.<BR><BR>5) Combine the skulls in to the new container and give the results to Roshawna. She will give you a new box and a note.<BR><BR>6) Give the box and note to Spiritist Roleko in Grimling Forest. He can be found at the large Vah Shir Outpost there. <BR><BR>This will spawn a Possessed Grimling and three Reanimated Grimlings. Kill them and loot their items.<BR><BR>7) Hand the items you just looted to Spiritist Roleko. He will give you a report in return.<BR><BR>8) Give the report to Scribe Cholsa(in the shaman guild) in Shar Vahl(+80, +150). She will give you a note.<BR><BR>9) Kill the Burning Priest in Scarlet Desert(+550, -750). He will drop an Amulet of Golden Rays.<BR><BR>10) Kill Thought Leeches in Mons Letalis(they are in cave near -1000,0) until one drops a Thought Leech Brain.<BR><BR>11) Kill Umbrous Toilers in Maiden's Eye until one drops Black Flame Charcoal.<BR><BR>12) Head back to Spiritist Roleko in Grimling Forest and hand him the Amulet of Golden Rays, Black Flame Charcoal, Thought Leech Brain and the note from Shar Vahl). This will spawn Rakshasa Karwoaro.<BR><BR>13) Kill Rakshasha and give his head to Spiritist Roleko. He will give you your shield.<br>


<br><table width="300" bgcolor="#004b97"><b><font color=#d2d200>Found in <a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqzone&eqzones.zone_name=%22Katta%20Castellum%22">Katta Castellum</a></b></font></table><br>
<b>Continent:</b> Luclin<br>
<b>Zone Type:</b> Town<br>
<b>Level Ranges:</b> 1 - 60<br>
<b>Connects To:</b> Tenebrous Mountains, Twilight Sea<br><br>

<b>Description:</b><br>This city has Bard, Cleric, Druid, Enchanter, Magician, Monk, Paladin, Ranger, Rogue, Shaman, Warrior and wizard guild halls.  It was built by the combine empire when they moved to Luclin.<br>


